The use of the term "spanning forest" suggests graph theory (cs.DS) as another likely sub-category. The problem is also related to partitioning (cs.DM) and combinatorial optimization (cs.GT). Finally, the NP-completeness results suggest complexity theory (cs.CC) as a possible sub-category.
